Add a Vendor
============

#. Click the <i class="fa fa-bars"></i> **menu icon** in the ribbon
#. Click **Finance**
#. Click **Expenses**
#. Click **Vendor**
#. Click the <i class="fa fa-plus"></i> **plus icon** in the upper right hand corner
#. Enter name of vendor
#. Enter address of vendor
#. Enter `Vendor ID </users/finance/guides/display_elements.html>`_
#. Click **Save**
#. If desired, `export </users/finance/guides/export_records.html>`_ vendor data
#. If desired, `edit </users/finance/guides/how_to_edit.html>`_ vendors
#. If desired, `merge </users/finance/guides/how_to_merge.html>`_ vendors
